<h2>lemon: Freshing Up your 'ggplot2' Plots</h2>
<p>Functions for working with legends and axis lines of 'ggplot2',
    facets that repeat axis lines on all panels, and some 'knitr' extensions.</p>
<table summary="Package lemon summary">
<tr>
